# <type>(<scope>): <subject>   — ≤50 characters, imperative mood, no period
#
# <body>  — what and why, not how. Blank line above. Wrap at ~72 characters.
#
# <footer> — BREAKING CHANGE: ...   |   Refs #123
#
# ── Types ───────────────────────────────────────────────
#   feat      new functionality
#   fix       bug fix
#   refactor  code change without behavior change
#   test      add/improve tests
#   docs      documentation only
#   chore     maintenance, dependencies, small tasks
#   ci        CI configuration
#   perf      performance
#   style     formatting/whitespace, no logic
#
# ── Scopes (layers) ─────────────────────────────────────
#   core  data  logic  gui  console  ci
#
# Example:  fix(data): keep save file when load fails
